The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 PCB may hire Young

Islamabad: Pakistan Cricket Board is contemplating the name of an American as fielding coach ahead of former South African great Jonty Rhodes for the national teams series against England. 

Mike Young, a former baseball player, coach and manager, who is presently working as a consultant with the New Zealand team on a three-week contract, may be roped in, a PCB official said. (PTI) 




